snippet.title: Flatout Stuntman for Android
snippet.description:
Have a take-off run with one of the many types and sorts of vehicles, launce your handpicked character (out of many, one even crazier as the other) and proceed to aim for the objects that will do you the most damage... thus earning you the most points! Try and take some coins along the way. Ragdoll fun for everone! This contains a ton of different and  fun themes, stunts, plenty of vehicles and numerous characters to have fun with.

Download the free game here:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.team6.FlatoutStuntman&feature=search_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwyLDEsImNvbS50ZWFtNi5GbGF0b3V0U3R1bnRtYW4iXQ..
